  <body>
    <segment id="1">

Cornucopia</segment>
    <segment id="13" parent="27" relname="interpretation">

Hans-Joachim Bosse, who is still a member of the city council responsible for finance, tried in vain to persuade the city councillors when the 2002 budget was presented.</segment>
    <segment id="2" parent="26" relname="concession">

In the run-up to their weekend retreat, the SPD budget politicians made a big splash with horror lists of possible savings items.
</segment>
    <segment id="3" parent="14" relname="interpretation"> 

In the end, however, everything remains the same:
</segment>
    <segment id="14" parent="26" relname="span">  

the fact that millions are missing does not prevent them from being distributed.</segment>
    <segment id="4" parent="24" relname="antithesis">

Bosse had recommended abandoning the expensive new theater building.
</segment>
    <segment id="5" parent="6" relname="reason">  

But the attempt to let the project die would have ended in disaster in view of the slim SPD-CDU majority.
</segment>
    <segment id="6" parent="24" relname="span">  

So the project was unanimously approved.
</segment>
    <segment id="7" parent="21" relname="span"> 

As with the Kammerakademie, the administration should make a few changes here and there,
</segment>
    <segment id="16" parent="7" relname="elaboration"> 

but nowhere should it really hurt.
</segment>
    <segment id="8" parent="23" relname="span">

Finally, the cornucopia is poured over daycare centers and schools.
</segment>
    <segment id="9" parent="22" relname="list"> 

Thanks to the cooperation agreement with the CDU, their approval is already in the bag.</segment>
    <segment id="10" parent="22" relname="list">  

The PDS will have nothing against it.
</segment>
    <segment id="11" parent="17" relname="purpose">  

In order to be able to make the necessary investments, however,

</segment>
    <segment id="17" parent="20" relname="span"> 
the only option will be to sell off the silverware.

</segment>
    <segment id="12" parent="19" relname="span"> 
This problem and the budget deficit will not disappear
</segment>
    <segment id="18" parent="12" relname="circumstance"> 
once the bosses have been sent into the desert.
</segment>
